:1736462,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T23:07:38.000Z","msg":"係呀  啱啱有隻扮勇武添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:29:34.000Z","msg":"who?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:32:40.000Z","msg":"一隊6人前線小隊宣布退出運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740008</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:34:35.000Z","msg":"P牌分化L, 唔好理佢"},{"pid":"bf7de7ad42c93611015ec135167d43756ae75d30","tid":1736462,"uid":312332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:35:03.000Z","msg":"連儂牆：絕對係 50歲以上人士既資訊來源<br />\n<br />\n無連儂牆後果<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無左連儂牆，佢地只會返去睇CCTVB</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">1：連儂牆位置分主區及副區</span></span><br />\n主區： 圖片要美化，排列要工整<br />\n副區：屬於隨時陣亡/被清洗區，唔洗太靚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆急需擴展<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>建議找尋真黃店，借佢半邊外牆興建連儂牆，記得要美圖，仲要好聲好氣問，可以拒絕</em></span><br />\n~借用位置不得高於一半，否則影響店舖透光<br />\n~借用大細可長可短，壁報板大細都可以<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">變相成為驗證真真真黃店!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做人要有禮貌，拒絕唔代表對方藍</span></span></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">最重要係內容</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請大家更改連儂牆內容<br />\n<br />\n警暴是果，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">貪腐政權是因</span><br />\n<br />\n我發現大家由6月反修例開始，比政府spin到去黑社會，再由黑社會spin到去警暴<br />\n<br />\n但係最終源頭，都係政權貪腐，勾結黑幫，包庇警暴，係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">官鄉警黑勾結</span></span><br />\n<br />\n連儂牆一定要 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Post大量政權貪污資訊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人一定要打岩政治旗號<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反貪污</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反黑社會</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反警暴</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">打黑反貪，反官鄉警黑勾結</span></span>"},{"pid":"4994e1f4b249cbb41c3aab22380d90f7db80b92b","tid":1736462,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a49300a53643f0a873d7260018b27c7883b3848","tid":1736462,"uid":111007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73362ffa1f688f49047e15a612437b8ebc738360","tid":1736462,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cd9f7554a407e41b1f2d323334305ad68f602fa","tid":1736462,"uid":111007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:29:34.000Z","msg":"who?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:32:40.000Z","msg":"一隊6人前線小隊宣布退出運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740008</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:34:35.000Z","msg":"P牌分化L, 唔好理佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"agger! 凌晨俾monpo dog推左上頂"},{"pid":"805fb06c6bce5c3eaa905948cde4d0582db794e1","tid":1736462,"uid":111007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4994e1f4b249cbb41c3aab22380d90f7db80b92b","tid":1736462,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a49300a53643f0a873d7260018b27c7883b3848","tid":1736462,"uid":111007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73362ffa1f688f49047e15a612437b8ebc738360","tid":1736462,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:32:40.000Z","msg":"一隊6人前線小隊宣布退出運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740008</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:34:35.000Z","msg":"P牌分化L, 唔好理佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"agger! 凌晨俾monpo dog推左上頂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:37:33.000Z","msg":"幫手做文宣OK? 內部士氣都好緊要"},{"pid":"a